{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "cosmic-watch-api",
    "name": "Cosmic Watch API",
    "description": "# üöÄ Cosmic Watch API Collection\n\nThis collection provides a comprehensive testing suite for the **Cosmic Watch** Near-Earth Object monitoring platform. It covers NASA's NeoWs API and the Supabase backend infrastructure including Auth, Database, and Realtime endpoints.\n\n## üõ†Ô∏è Setup Instructions\n1.  **Environment Variables**: Set the `supabase_url`, `supabase_anon_key`, and `nasa_api_key` in the collection variables.\n2.  **Authentication**: Run the `Sign In` request first. It includes a test script that automatically captures the `access_token` and sets it as a collection variable for all subsequent requests.\n3.  **NASA API**: You can use `DEMO_KEY` for basic testing, but a personalized API key from [api.nasa.gov](https://api.nasa.gov) is recommended for higher rate limits.\n\n## üìÇ Folders\n- **NASA API**: Testing core asteroid feed and specific object lookup.\n- **Authentication**: Managing user accounts (Sign Up, Sign In, Sign Out, Profile Info).\n- **Asteroids (Cache)**: Querying the synced local asteroid data.\n- **Watchlist**: Managing user-specific tracked objects.\n- **Community Hub**: Interacting with the global research forum.\n- **Profile Management**: Updating researcher avatars and usernames.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "supabase_url",
      "value": "https://your-project.supabase.co",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "supabase_anon_key",
      "value": "your-anon-key",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "nasa_api_key",
      "value": "DEMO_KEY",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "test_user_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "NASA API",
      "description": "Direct integration with NASA Near-Earth Object Web Service (NeoWs).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get NEO Feed",
          "description": "Fetch a list of asteroids based on their closest approach date to Earth.",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "https://api.nasa.gov/neo/rest/v1/feed?start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-01-07&api_key={{nasa_api_key}}",
              "protocol": "https",
              "host": [
                "api",
                "nasa",
                "gov"
              ],
              "path": [
                "neo",
                "rest",
                "v1",
                "feed"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "start_date",
                  "value": "2024-01-01"
                },
                {
                  "key": "end_date",
                  "value": "2024-01-07"
                },
                {
                  "key": "api_key",
                  "value": "{{nasa_api_key}}"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get NEO Lookup",
          "description": "Lookup a specific Near Earth Object by its NASA ID.",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "https://api.nasa.gov/neo/rest/v1/neo/3542519?api_key={{nasa_api_key}}",
              "protocol": "https",
              "host": [
                "api",
                "nasa",
                "gov"
              ],
              "path": [
                "neo",
                "rest",
                "v1",
                "neo",
                "3542519"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "api_key",
                  "value": "{{nasa_api_key}}"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "description": "Endpoints managed by Supabase Auth (GoTrue).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Sign Up",
          "description": "Register a new researcher account. Requires a strong password (8+ chars, number, special char).",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"researcher@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"username\": \"astro_pioneer\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/auth/v1/signup",
              "host": [
                "{{supabase_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "v1",
                "signup"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Sign In",
          "description": "Authenticate an existing user. Retrieves a JWT token which is automatically saved to the `access_token` variable.",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"researcher@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/auth/v1/token?grant_type=password",
              "host": [
                "{{supabase_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "v1",
                "token"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "password"
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Sign In Successful\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"access_token\", jsonData.access_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"test_user_id\", jsonData.user.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User Info",
          "description": "Get data of the currently authenticated user session.",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/auth/v1/user",
              "host": [
                "{{supabase_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "v1",
                "user"
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Asteroids (Synced Cache)",
      "description": "Read-only access to the synced NASA data stored in Supabase.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List All Asteroids",
          "description": "Fetch paginated cached asteroids ordered by risk score.",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/rest/v1/asteroids_cache?select=*&order=risk_score.desc&limit=20",
              "host": [
                "{{supabase_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "rest",
                "v1",
                "asteroids_cache"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "select",
                  "value": "*"
                },
                {
                  "key": "order",
                  "value": "risk_score.desc"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hazardous Alert Filter",
          "description": "Query only potentially hazardous objects.",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/rest/v1/asteroids_cache?select=*&is_potentially_hazardous=eq.true",
              "host": [
                "{{supabase_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "rest",
                "v1",
                "asteroids_cache"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "select",
                  "value": "*"
                },
                {
                  "key": "is_potentially_hazardous",
                  "value": "eq.true"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Community Hub",
      "description": "Interactions for the real-time global research chat.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Discussion Hub Messages",
          "description": "Fetch latest messages from the community hub.",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/rest/v1/community_messages?select=*&order=created_at.desc&limit=50",
              "host": [
                "{{supabase_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "rest",
                "v1",
                "community_messages"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "select",
                  "value": "*"
                },
                {
                  "key": "order",
                  "value": "created_at.desc"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "50"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Send Signal (Post Message)",
          "description": "Broadcast a message to all researchers. Requires Authentication.",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"user_id\": \"{{test_user_id}}\",\n  \"username\": \"astro_pioneer\",\n  \"message\": \"I've detected significant orbital variance in NEO-3542519!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/rest/v1/community_messages",
              "host": [
                "{{supabase_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "rest",
                "v1",
                "community_messages"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Retract Signal (Delete Message)",
          "description": "Delete a message sent by the user. RLS policies ensure you can only delete your own messages.",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/rest/v1/community_messages?id=eq.YOUR_MESSAGE_UUID&user_id=eq.{{test_user_id}}",
              "host": [
                "{{supabase_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "rest",
                "v1",
                "community_messages"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "eq.YOUR_MESSAGE_UUID"
                },
                {
                  "key": "user_id",
                  "value": "eq.{{test_user_id}}"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Researcher Profiles",
      "description": "Managing your public researcher identity.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get My Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/rest/v1/profiles?id=eq.{{test_user_id}}&select=*",
              "host": [
                "{{supabase_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "rest",
                "v1",
                "profiles"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "eq.{{test_user_id}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "select",
                  "value": "*"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Profile",
          "description": "Update your researcher username or avatar URL.",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"senior_researcher_v2\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabase_url}}/rest/v1/profiles?id=eq.{{test_user_id}}",
              "host": [
                "{{supabase_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "rest",
                "v1",
                "profiles"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "eq.{{test_user_id}}"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}